<li id="cite_note-14"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-14">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Some sources say he started a software company first.<sup id="cite_ref-directory_11-3" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-directory-11">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup></span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-19"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-19">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Sources conflict on whether total layoffs were 20%, 27%, or 30%.</span>
