<li id="cite_note-GNW-51"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-GNW_51-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://globenewswire.com/news-release/2015/08/10/759326/10145310/en/Consulting-Magazine-Announces-Its-Excellence-in-Social-Community-Investment-Awards-Winners.html">"Consulting Magazine Announces Its Excellence in Social Community Investment Awards Winners"</a>. <i>Global News Wire</i><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">2018-02-02</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Global+News+Wire&amp;rft.atitle=Consulting+Magazine+Announces+Its+Excellence+in+Social+Community+Investment+Awards+Winners&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fglobenewswire.com%2Fnews-release%2F2015%2F08%2F10%2F759326%2F10145310%2Fen%2FConsulting-Magazine-Announces-Its-Excellence-in-Social-Community-Investment-Awards-Winners.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABain+%26+Company" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/></span>
