<li id="cite_note-Weller_Jacobs_2016-60"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Weller_Jacobs_2016_60-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFWellerJacobs2016" class="citation web">Weller, Chris; Jacobs, Sarah (December 8, 2016). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.businessinsider.com/bain-office-tour-2017-2016-12">"Bain &amp; Company was just named the best workplace of 2017"</a>. <i>Business Insider</i><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">July 3,</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Business+Insider&amp;rft.atitle=Bain+%26+Company+was+just+named+the+best+workplace+of+2017&amp;rft.date=2016-12-08&amp;rft.aulast=Weller&amp;rft.aufirst=Chris&amp;rft.au=Jacobs%2C+Sarah&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbain-office-tour-2017-2016-12&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABain+%26+Company" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/></span>
